defs.name: DecodeError
defs.value:
enum DecodeError {
    Overflow,
    LeadingZero,
    InputTooShort,
    NonCanonicalSingleByte,
    NonCanonicalSize,
    UnexpectedLength,
    UnexpectedString,
    UnexpectedList,
    ListLengthMismatch {
            expected: usize,
            got: usize,
        },
    Custom(&'static str),
}
